# SRS Addendum 3 — Cross-Cutting Concerns

## CrispyTivi — Offline, Multi-Device, Notifications, Error Handling, Performance, Widgets, Sharing, Radio, and Theming

**Supplements**: `.ai/SRS.md`, `.ai/SRS-ADDENDUM.md`, `.ai/SRS-ADDENDUM-2.md`
**Date**: 2026-03-14

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Offline & Network Degradation](#1-offline--network-degradation)
2. [Multi-Device Handoff & Casting](#2-multi-device-handoff--casting)
3. [Notification System](#3-notification-system)
4. [Deep Linking & Voice Assistants](#4-deep-linking--voice-assistants)
5. [Error States & Recovery](#5-error-states--recovery)
6. [Performance & Resource Budgets](#6-performance--resource-budgets)
7. [Home Screen Widgets & System Integration](#7-home-screen-widgets--system-integration)
8. [Sharing & Social Features](#8-sharing--social-features)
9. [Audio-Only / Radio Experience](#9-audio-only--radio-experience)
10. [Theming & Whitelabel](#10-theming--whitelabel)

