# SRS Addendum 4 — Security, Privacy, Localization, Analytics, Parental Controls, Backup, Deployment & Legal

## CrispyTivi — Technology-Agnostic Requirements

**Supplements**: `.ai/SRS.md`, `.ai/SRS-ADDENDUM.md`, `.ai/SRS-ADDENDUM-2.md`, `.ai/SRS-ADDENDUM-3.md`
**Date**: 2026-03-14

---

## Table of Contents

1. [Security & Privacy](#1-security--privacy)
2. [Localization & Internationalization](#2-localization--internationalization)
3. [Analytics & Telemetry](#3-analytics--telemetry)
4. [Parental Controls (Deep Dive)](#4-parental-controls-deep-dive)
5. [Backup, Restore & Migration](#5-backup-restore--migration)
6. [Deployment & Distribution](#6-deployment--distribution)
7. [Licensing & Legal](#7-licensing--legal)
8. [Diagnostics & Observability](#8-diagnostics--observability)

