| 6-platform support (phone, tablet, TV, desktop, web) | Eliminates TiviMate's Android-only limitation |
| Unified IPTV + Plex + Emby + Jellyfin | Single app replaces 2-3 apps per household |
| Multi-profile with full RBAC | Household-ready from day one |
| All IPTV protocols (M3U + Xtream + Stalker) | No provider lock-in unlike TiviMate (Xtream-heavy) |
